title: WindTunnel® 2 Rewind Bagless Upright: Loss of suction/won't
description:
Hi cdubb! I read your review on Hoover.com about loss of suction on your WindTunnel. It sounds like an easy fix. I put together a quick video with some tips to help restore strong sealed suction to your vacuum. Let me know if you need any more help!

-Wil
